Amazon Simple Notification Service (SNS):
----------------------------------------
It is a web service that automates the process of sending notifications to subscribers. It is a fully managed messaging service for both applications-to-application (A2A) and application-to-person (A2P) communication. 
SNS provides developers with the following capabilities: 
Scalable
Cost-effective
Flexible
Publish messages from an application
Deliver messages to subscribers or other applications
SNS enables decoupling of microservices, distributed systems, and serverless applications by providing publish-subscribe (pub-sub) and point-to-point communication patterns. 
SNS is designed to make web-scale computing easier for developers.
